ğŸ” 7ï¸âƒ£ Regular Expressions (Regex)

Regex = powerful pattern matching.

Example:

import re

pattern = r"\d+\.\d+\.\d+\.\d+"
match = re.findall(pattern, "Login from 10.0.0.1")
print(match)


ğŸ”¥ This extracts IPs from text logs.

ğŸ“‚ 8ï¸âƒ£ File Handling (Open/Read files)

