ğŸ›¡ï¸ 10ï¸âƒ£ Real Cybersecurity Python Examples
Example: Count failed login entries
count = 0
with open("auth.log","r") as f:
    for line in f:
        if "failed" in line:
            count += 1
print("Failed count:", count)

Example: Extract IP addresses
import re

ips = []
with open("auth.log","r") as f:
    for line in f:
        found = re.findall(r"\d+\.\d+\.\d+\.\d+", line)
        ips.extend(found)
print(set(ips))  # unique IPs

